# API测试文件 (使用REST Client扩展)
# 或直接复制curl命令到终端执行

### 1. 获取配额状态
GET http://localhost:3000/api/quota
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. 获取相册列表
GET http://localhost:3000/api/albums
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. 创建新相册
POST http://localhost:3000/api/albums
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试相册",
  "description": "这是一个测试相册",
  "isPublic": false
}

### 4. 获取会员计划
GET http://localhost:3000/api/membership/plans
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. 创建订阅
POST http://localhost:3000/api/membership/subscribe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planId": "basic",
  "billingCycle": "monthly",
  "paymentMethod": "stripe"
}

### 6. 创建支付会话
POST http://localhost:3000/api/payment/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planId": "basic",
  "billingCycle": "monthly",
  "provider": "stripe"
}
